az ir zent avek fun Hilperts, un vi azoy hot ir zikh gekent mit Malemants?

00:13:18.840 --> 00:13:22.276
ikh bin gekumen tsu mayn FRIEND nokh Brisl,

00:13:24.105 --> 00:13:27.862
hobn zey gezitsn mitn kind un der man,

00:13:29.185 --> 00:13:31.147
un zey hobn gornisht getun.

00:13:31.147 --> 00:13:33.684
zi hot geputst, zi hot nor geputst.

00:13:34.821 --> 00:13:36.345
zog ikh tsu ir,

00:13:36.345 --> 00:13:38.021
"vos putstu?

00:13:38.297 --> 00:13:40.535
gey zukh

00:13:40.795 --> 00:13:43.219
du zolst aroys fun danet!

00:13:43.731 --> 00:13:46.796
zay nisht do mer, gey avek fun di shtub!"

00:13:47.798 --> 00:13:50.272
zogt zi, zi veyst nisht vu tsu geyn.

00:13:50.734 --> 00:13:53.867
hob ikh ir gezogt, ikh hob ir nisht gezogt vu ikh voyn,

00:13:54.126 --> 00:13:56.381
ikh hob ir gezogt, "veyst vos?

00:13:56.387 --> 00:13:59.117
gey dortn nokh Stokel,

00:13:59.117 --> 00:14:01.742
nokh, in geb a kuk

00:14:01.742 --> 00:14:03.638
dortn iz do

00:14:04.183 --> 00:14:06.475
dires tsu fardingen,

00:14:06.475 --> 00:14:11.265
un geb avek un ding dir a shtub un gey aroys fun danet!"

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:16.563
zene- ober dos tsveyte mol ikh bin gekumen, NO.

00:14:17.329 --> 00:14:20.090
bin ikh gekumen eyn mol

00:14:20.265 --> 00:14:22.031
hot zi mir gezogt,

00:14:22.392 --> 00:14:24.563
az zi hot gedungen

00:14:25.041 --> 00:14:30.640
Hil- der Molemants hot farkoyft a hoyz vos er hot dos aleyn oyfgeboyt,

00:14:30.640 --> 00:14:34.958
iz dos hoyz geshtanen in gantsn leydik, hot zi dos oysgedungen.

00:14:36.381 --> 00:14:39.162
un zi hot aroysgeshtelt di FURNITURES,

00:14:39.162 --> 00:14:40.672
zi hot badekt di

00:14:40.672 --> 00:14:42.410
CH- CHAIRS mit

00:14:42.410 --> 00:14:44.300
gazet PAPERS,

00:14:44.300 --> 00:14:46.348
un zi iz gekumen oproymen.

00:14:47.586 --> 00:14:50.769
eyn mol hot zi gezen az ikh klap

00:14:50.843 --> 00:14:52.794
bay Molemants untn,

00:14:52.834 --> 00:14:54.881
zi hot geven in der heykh

00:14:54.881 --> 00:14:57.975
un ikh bin do geven arayntsugeyn tsu Molemants.

00:14:58.504 --> 00:15:02.430
ikh hob mikh zeyer shnel bafroyndet mit mentshn.

00:15:03.178 --> 00:15:04.539
makht zi

00:15:04.866 --> 00:15:08.356
sh- fun dro- a- oyvn UNK aropgeshrign

00:15:08.356 --> 00:15:11.374
tsu Molemants az m'zol mikh nisht araynlozn.

00:15:12.713 --> 00:15:15.424
hot Molemants nor geentfert,

00:15:15.548 --> 00:15:18.377
az enk tsvishn enk

00:15:18.703 --> 00:15:21.464
kenen zikh nisht farshtendikn,

00:15:21.471 --> 00:15:23.642
tu far vos kumstu tsu mir?

00:15:26.888 --> 00:15:32.149
ikh nem dikh arayn, tsu ir in di heykh, take tsu di vos ikh hob gezogt

00:15:32.149 --> 00:15:33.988
zi zol aroysgeyn fun ir shtub,

00:15:33.988 --> 00:15:38.306
un du lozt ir nisht arayngeyn tsu mir in shtub arayn?!

00:15:38.565 --> 00:15:40.736
un ikh hob shoyn bay im gegat a ROOM!

00:15:44.995 --> 00:15:47.436
MONSIEUR, s'hot nisht lang gedoyert,

00:15:47.796 --> 00:15:48.535
hot

00:15:48.535 --> 00:15:53.746
frier nokh hot men im aro- hot men nor aroysgenumen mitn ki- kind,

00:15:54.293 --> 00:15:56.447
un er iz antlofn,

00:15:56.571 --> 00:16:06.338
u ven m'hot zi genumen mitn kind, vayl er iz shpeter gekumen dortn shlofn, un mayn man hot nor gevolt aropgeyn fun der MANSARDE,

00:16:06.338 --> 00:16:08.512
un nor redn mit Mendl.

00:16:08.535 --> 00:16:17.287
zog ikh, "Simon, zolst zayn shtil, un du zolst nisht geyn m'zol dikh farbrenen, zolst zayn ruik!"

00:16:19.032 --> 00:16:21.101
iz er nisht aropgeganen.

00:16:21.107 --> 00:16:27.699
nor Mendl iz gekumen, er hot gehat a pak mit gelt bay zikh in dem hoyz untern bet,

00:16:28.161 --> 00:16:31.749
az m'zol aroysnemen di froy mitn kind fun Malin,

00:16:32.363 --> 00:16:35.394
iz er avekgeganen mit zayn shvester,

00:16:35.923 --> 00:16:39.005
er hot mitgenumen der pak mit gelt,

00:16:39.231 --> 00:16:42.054
hot men tsugenumen dem pak mit gelt,

00:16:42.054 --> 00:16:45.469
un m'hot tsugenumen dem Mendl mit di shvester.

00:16:46.318 --> 00:16:48.112
azoy zenen mentshn geven.

00:16:48.112 --> 00:16:50.379
ikh geb ir a guter rat,

00:16:50.892 --> 00:16:53.394
un ikh zog ir alesding,

00:16:53.394 --> 00:16:56.150
vos zi volt mir dos nisht getun,

00:16:56.578 --> 00:17:01.381
un zi tut di shtu- di di CHAIRS iz zi gekumen putsn!

00:17:02.164 --> 00:17:03.001
nu!

00:17:04.392 --> 00:17:07.136
far dem, vos hot ir mikh gefregt?

00:17:08.357 --> 00:17:11.979
NO veg- vegn Molemants, vi azoy ir zent ongekumen dortn.

00:17:11.547 --> 00:17:15.236
ah bin ikh gekumen nokh di froy,

00:17:15.462 --> 00:17:23.725
bin ikh gekumen tsu dem Molemants, vayl zi hot mir gezogt vu zi hot gedungen un vos hot getun.

00:17:23.915 --> 00:17:27.503
iz nakher bin ikh gekumen tsu Molemants.

00:17:29.198 --> 00:17:35.030
un genoy vu zent ir geven bay der Molemants, in a vos far a tsimer, vi azoy?

00:17:33.855 --> 00:17:35.857
neyn in a MANSARDE.

00:17:35.897 --> 00:17:39.570
ober m'iz geven hintn a sakh mit zey,

00:17:39.947 --> 00:17:44.986
un mayn man hot geshpilt mit dem altn Molemants in ASMOZIAS,

00:17:45.010 --> 00:17:46.337
un gekokht,

00:17:46.461 --> 00:17:48.649
ven zi hot gekokht far zikh,

00:17:48.790 --> 00:17:52.361
hot zi ge- hot men arayngeleygt in der zelber top,

00:17:53.059 --> 00:17:59.313
flegt aroysgeyn fun dem hoyz durkh di anderthalbn yorn, tsi ir hot geblibn ineveynik di gantse tsayt?

00:17:59.522 --> 00:18:02.604
v- ikh bin aroysgeganen, mayn man iz geblibn.

00:18:03.133 --> 00:18:06.615
bay der nakht s'geven fintster ze'men aroysgeganen.

00:18:06.615 --> 00:18:10.142
di ve- di fentster in dem MANSARDE iz geven fardekt

00:18:10.142 --> 00:18:11.610
mit shvarts,

00:18:11.610 --> 00:18:14.588
ikh hob aropgekukt a mol, gegebn a khap,

00:18:14.588 --> 00:18:20.258
hob ikh gezen a hunt mit a kats, oy! zog ikh, ven ikh bin a hunt un a kats, gey ikh dokh yetst

00:18:20.258 --> 00:18:22.584
in droysn, hob ikh dokh nisht keyn moyre.

00:18:22.658 --> 00:18:25.723
un ir veyst, ikh hob ale fraytik tsu nakhts

00:18:25.746 --> 00:18:27.413
getsundn likht,

00:18:27.413 --> 00:18:29.132
far mayn tatishi,

00:18:29.391 --> 00:18:31.598
dos muter gebetn

00:18:31.598 --> 00:18:33.755
vayl zi hot mikh zeyer lib gegat,

00:18:33.998 --> 00:18:40.236
az zi zol zen az m'zol bafrayt vern, m'zol kenen tsurik aheym, dos hob ikh gebetn.

00:18:40.292 --> 00:18:41.672
un di shikse,

00:18:41.672 --> 00:18:52.858
Molemants hot gegat a tokhter, zi hot mir aroysgenumen fun yeder likht di bendlekh, di katn, un zi hot mir gemakht frishe likht.

00:18:54.754 --> 00:18:56.194
s'iz shoyn shpeter.

00:18:56.194 --> 00:18:57.094
neyn?

00:18:57.943 --> 00:19:01.610
iz zi hot mir gemakht likht un ikh hob gebentsht di likht.

00:19:01.610 --> 00:19:04.901
hobn zey nokh gezogt, "Sena, kuk zi hot nervn!

00:19:04.901 --> 00:19:07.336
"zi iz bahaltn un bentsht likht!"

00:19:07.815 --> 00:19:09.786
zog ikh, "ikh bentsh likht vayl ikh,

00:19:09.786 --> 00:19:11.470
I PRAY GOD,

00:19:11.494 --> 00:19:15.203
s- nisht nor far mir, far enk oykhet!

00:19:15.203 --> 00:19:18.440
ets vilt dokh oykh nisht az zey zoln do zayn."

00:19:21.990 --> 00:19:24.144
ikh hob zeyer gut mit zey gelebt.

00:19:23.847 --> 00:19:25.511
ikh hob gevolt fregn,

00:19:25.770 --> 00:19:29.729
az ir hot batsolt Hilperts un Malemants,

00:19:30.343 --> 00:19:32.497
vu iz geven ayer gelt?

00:19:32.892 --> 00:19:35.282
vu hot ir zikh bahaltn, dos bahaltn?

00:19:34.162 --> 00:19:35.200
bay goyim.

00:19:35.845 --> 00:19:38.218
dos gelt iz geven bahaltn bay goyim?

00:19:37.330 --> 00:19:43.483
dos gelt iz geven bahaltn bay goyim, der dokter hot oykhet gehat gelt far di kinder,

00:19:43.523 --> 00:19:45.660
BUT kh'eb aykh zogn,

00:19:45.767 --> 00:19:50.447
oyf dakht zikh, ober s'iz nisht dakht zikh nor SURE,

00:19:50.447 --> 00:19:53.569
undz hot mir gegat gelt mit zikh oykhet.

00:19:53.569 --> 00:19:55.509
ober keyner hot nisht gevust.

00:19:55.509 --> 00:19:59.159
s'iz gelign oyf der MANSARDE bagrobn in der erd.

00:20:02.727 --> 00:20:05.809
un zey hobn nisht gevust az s- az es gefint zikh dort.

00:20:04.701 --> 00:20:05.786
akh!

00:20:05.786 --> 00:20:07.313
keyner hot nisht gevust.

00:20:07.313 --> 00:20:11.630
ikh hob mikh nisht gefirt az ikh makh fish shabes,

00:20:11.637 --> 00:20:13.926
az ikh tants shabes,

00:20:13.982 --> 00:20:16.999
ales vos Moylemants hot gegesn

00:20:16.999 --> 00:20:19.714
un vos Moylemants hot gekokht,

00:20:19.720 --> 00:20:23.578
hob ikh gegesn. ikh zog aykh, ikh bin gegangen Hilperts nokh

00:20:23.854 --> 00:20:28.337
un er hot gekoyft zup un s'geven vantsn ineveynik,

00:20:28.478 --> 00:20:31.256
gegesn, nisht gezogt az s'toyg nisht,

00:20:33.372 --> 00:20:35.020
ikh hob mikh gefirt

00:20:35.447 --> 00:20:36.656
in ordenung.

00:20:37.607 --> 00:20:42.950
durkh der tsayt vos ir zent geven bay der Molemants zent ir geven in farbindung mit di kinder a mol?

00:20:43.092 --> 00:20:45.603
a sakh mol, ikh bin gegan,

00:20:45.603 --> 00:20:47.844
ikh hob mir ayngeshtelt dos lebn,

00:20:48.087 --> 00:20:50.426
ikh hob zey getrogn nokh oranzhes,

00:20:50.803 --> 00:20:53.162
un aroyfgekumen iz di

00:20:53.162 --> 00:20:54.951
doytshe politsey,

00:20:54.951 --> 00:20:58.357
un er hot geheysn ale aropgeyn oytobus.

00:20:59.258 --> 00:21:02.796
un ikh bin do gegan azoy ongetun mit a ⟨tslom⟩,

00:21:03.105 --> 00:21:04.246
un

00:21:04.590 --> 00:21:06.896
un aza kr- kra- CROISE,

00:21:07.442 --> 00:21:09.478
un ikh hob oyfgemakht

00:21:09.973 --> 00:21:13.392
dem, ikh bin tsugeganen, zog ikh, yetst gey ikh shoyn

00:21:14.040 --> 00:21:15.902
oyf eybik avek dakht zikh.

00:21:15.902 --> 00:21:18.256
un ikh hob oyfgemakht di di

00:21:18.256 --> 00:21:21.122
di SACOCHE, ale hobn gemuzt efenen,

00:21:21.432 --> 00:21:24.188
hobn zey nokh gezogt, oranzhes, oranzhes,

00:21:24.188 --> 00:21:26.837
ikh, un m'hot mikh bald gelozt aroyf tsurik.

00:21:26.837 --> 00:21:29.981
nor nokh dem bin ikh shoyn nisht getrogn keyn oranzhes.

00:21:30.308 --> 00:21:32.107
ikh hob nokh dos

00:21:33.109 --> 00:21:34.672
vos di kni

00:21:34.864 --> 00:21:36.582
shoklt zikh mir,

00:21:36.582 --> 00:21:37.907
tut mir vey,

00:21:37.907 --> 00:21:43.886
vayl ikh hob nisht shoyn nisht gekent geyn, ikh bin dokh geven geli- gezitsn,

00:21:43.977 --> 00:21:48.915
m'hot dokh, bay der s'geven fintster, ze'men a bisl aroysgeganen.

00:21:49.225 --> 00:21:50.200
un do,

00:21:50.200 --> 00:21:53.690
vos nisht far aykh gedakht, shtikt mir zeyer shtark.

00:21:53.916 --> 00:21:57.032
dos hob ikh gekrogn mit di oranzhes.

00:21:58.810 --> 00:22:00.829
vos heyst az ir hot gekrogn?

00:22:00.649 --> 00:22:02.958
ikh hob gekrogn, vos tut mir

00:22:02.958 --> 00:22:05.334
az s'shtikt mir keseyder do,

00:22:06.488 --> 00:22:09.300
ven ikh gey tsum dokter zog ikh im oykhet.

00:22:09.728 --> 00:22:11.966
az do shikt.

00:22:14.503 --> 00:22:18.699
nu yetst, veyst, ikh hob ongehoybn tsu forn in beder,

00:22:18.790 --> 00:22:21.208
ikh hob ongehoybn mikh tsu flegn,

00:22:21.208 --> 00:22:23.171
dos hot a sakh tsu zogn.

00:22:24.527 --> 00:22:26.642
s'iz nokh epes tsu dertseyln

00:22:26.642 --> 00:22:30.782
epes vos iz geshen oder mit Hilperts oder mit Molemants?

00:22:31.345 --> 00:22:34.427
vos iz geshen? zey zenen geshtorbn,

00:22:34.483 --> 00:22:37.104
un ikh hob gemeynt az nokh di krig

00:22:37.104 --> 00:22:40.968
vel ikh makhn un tsuzamen nemen di gantse shtetl

00:22:40.968 --> 00:22:46.031
mit a, mit a galekh, mit a kroyn,

00:22:46.031 --> 00:22:47.769
un ikh vel zey firn

00:22:47.769 --> 00:22:50.174
un ikh vel zey firn oyf di CEMETARY,

00:22:50.174 --> 00:22:53.647
un ikh vel ale zogn vos zey hobn far undz getun.

00:22:54.835 --> 00:22:57.529
zent ir a mol tsurik geforn keyn Varshe?

00:22:58.564 --> 00:22:59.199
Varshe?!

00:22:58.632 --> 00:22:59.250
ye,

00:22:59.644 --> 00:23:04.143
ven, vo- ven ir get mir gants Varshe,

00:23:04.572 --> 00:23:09.150
volt ikh geven gegan, volt ikh geven geforn nokh Varshe, nokh Poyln?!

00:23:09.150 --> 00:23:10.573
tsu di polyakn?!

00:23:11.102 --> 00:23:13.340
NEVER! NEVER!

00:23:13.363 --> 00:23:14.808
zent ir tsurik,

00:23:13.431 --> 00:23:17.036
ikh volt mikh geshemt tsu di polyakn tsu forn.

00:23:16.249 --> 00:23:19.005
zent ir a mol tsurik keyn keyn BRUSSELS?

