afilek mayne kinder zenen geforn un zey hobn gevizn zeyere kinder vu m'iz geven bahaltn in BRUSSELS, un alts dertseylt. di kinder zenen oft geforn, vayl zey hobn geven in di shuln, zey hobn bazukht di profesorn zeyere,

00:23:39.162 --> 00:23:41.909
zeyer oft, ikh bin oykh geven zeyer oft.

