az vos iz geshen,

00:23:53.543 --> 00:23:59.747
di di krig hot zikh farendikt dortn in Belgye in in in in fir un fertsik,

00:24:00.360 --> 00:24:01.875
az ven zent ir,

00:24:01.875 --> 00:24:03.307
vu zayt ir geven?

00:24:03.752 --> 00:24:05.096
in Belgye?

00:24:03.820 --> 00:24:05.417
nokhn nokhn krig.

00:24:05.659 --> 00:24:09.163
vu ikh bin geven in nokh der krig? ale mol in Belgye.

