ikh hob nisht DEMENAGEirt fun BRUSSELS.

00:24:58.427 --> 00:25:01.273
un vos hot ir geton durkh di yorn?

00:25:01.650 --> 00:25:03.635
mayn man iz gevezn a

00:25:04.114 --> 00:25:06.234
keyneynore a raykher mentsh,

00:25:06.240 --> 00:25:08.967
m'iz gekumen, hot er do gekoyft dray hayzer,

00:25:10.476 --> 00:25:12.118
nokh Kanade.

00:25:10.510 --> 00:25:12.090
az far vos zent ir,

00:25:12.096 --> 00:25:13.895
far vos zent ir avek

00:25:14.188 --> 00:25:18.198
keyn fun fun Belgye in tsvey un fuftsikstn yor?

00:25:18.677 --> 00:25:22.096
ikh bin nisht avek tsvey un fuftsikstn yor fun Belgye.

00:25:20.415 --> 00:25:21.776
in eyn un fuftsik?

