ikh hob shpeter khasene gehat, ikh hob geven in Antverpn,

00:25:27.570 --> 00:25:29.977
ikh hob shpeter khasene gehat,

00:25:30.388 --> 00:25:33.920
un ikh bin tsurikgeforn mit mayn man nokh BRUSSELS,

00:25:33.920 --> 00:25:36.021
un ikh hob geboyrn di kinder,

00:25:36.021 --> 00:25:38.705
un dentsmolt hot men geboyt dos hoyz oyf

00:25:38.705 --> 00:25:40.536
RUE PHILIPPE DE CHAMPAGNE,

00:25:40.536 --> 00:25:41.942
dos iz gevezn

00:25:42.015 --> 00:25:50.564
GARDINORIE, GARDIMIDIE, un m'hot dortn gevoynt, MONSIEUR, biz ikh avekgeforn do nokh

00:25:50.976 --> 00:25:52.337
nokh CANADA.

